Title: On the ambiguities in the effective action in Lorentz-violating gravity
Authors: M. Gomes and T. Mariz and J. R. Nascimento and E. Passos and A. Yu. Petrov and A. J. da Silva
Abstract: We investigate the occurrence of ambiguities for Lorentz-violating gravitational Chern-Simons term. It turns out that this term is accompanied by a coefficient depending on an undetermined parameter, due to an arbitrariness in the choice of the conserved current.
